Icon Genuine Earphone Type - C White (IEP-201)
description:
The Icon Genuine Earphone Type-C (IEP-201) is a wired earphone designed with a Type-C connector. It's equipped with noise control features to help reduce background sounds, although it's not as effective as premium noise-canceling models. The earphone is lightweight, featuring a 1.2-meter tensile wire cable for durability and ease of use. It also comes with silicone earplugs in different sizes for a comfortable fit.Ingredients: This is an electronics product, so it includes materials such as plastic, rubber for the ear tips, and copper wire for the cable.Use: Ideal for listening to music, taking calls, and enjoying media on Type-C compatible devices like smartphones, tablets, and laptops. The noise control feature can enhance the listening experience by minimizing ambient noise. Model: IEP-201.Plug : Type-C.Speaker : 1045.Cable Length: 1.2 m.Cable : Tensile Wire.Accessories : S / L silicone earplugs each set.Noise Control.
